I"¸<h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>

<p>Use when you want to disable access to an interface feature or element, but still want to maintain the elementâ€™s visibility to the user.</p>

<div class="grid-2">
<div>
    <p class="example"><img src="../images/inactive/inactive-do.svg" alt="Example of an inactive checkbox inside an active checkbox" /></p>

    <div class="do">
      <p><img src="../images/global/check.svg" alt="Checkmark icon indicating a good choice" /> Do</p>
